node.text: Freaking the freak out! What the what! Ahhh! My @tula product is HERE! I think I’m still in shock! Coolest experience ever! We took summertime and put it in a tube! Picture yourself sitting on the beach in Hawaii with the sand on your skin, drink in your hand, flowers surrounding you, & breathing in the fresh sweet air. Got it? Good. Cuz this sugar scrub smells even better than that! So refreshing hibiscus lemonade exfoliating sugar scrub is by far Tula’s best smelling product 🌺🍋 annnd bonus! It’ll leave your skin smoother than Kamp’s booty! You can get it through the link in my stories right now and my discount code KRISTA will get ya 15% off! I could literally squeeze the crap out of each and every one of you who have rooted me on, messaged me, posted about it, purchased it & told your friend about it. Now let’s all go grab a Malibu & diet together to celebrate! 🥳 #tulapartner
